  <ability>
    <abilitytitle>Countless Bites</abilitytitle>
    <abilityid>monster.countless_bites</abilityid>
    <abilityactiontype><standard/></abilityactiontype>
    <tags><npc/><monster/><mettlepool/></tags>
    <abilityranks from="1" to="4"/>
    <gmgability/>
    <abilitycheck dc="5"  dmg="2+Rank">Mettle+Endurance</abilitycheck>
    <spline></spline>
    <abilitydescription>
      <p noindent="true">
	The monster makes dozens of attacks per round.  No to-hit
	roll is required.  No block or dodge saves apply.  The monster does
	a fixed amount of damage to each character, friend or foe, adjacent
	to it at the end of the monsters turn equal to the abilities Rank.  The monster
	makes an automatic attack when making an opportunity attack.  The
	characters are Dazed and Distracted.
      </p>

      <p>
	On the first round characters have to make a mettle check to ignore the
	bites or lose their turn.
      </p>
    </abilitydescription>
  </ability>

